snippet.title: Warcraft III: Reign Of Chaos Intro Cinematics
snippet.description:
WC3:ROC opens with the Horde leader Thrall waking from a nightmare warning him that the return of the Burning Legion is imminent. After a brief encounter with a man called "the Prophet", and fearing that his dream was more of a vision than a nightmare, he leads his forces in an exodus from Lordaeron to the forgotten lands of Kalimdor.
